# WashFlow — Manual QA Regression Prompt

> **For:** GPT Atlas (or any LLM-based QA agent)
> **App URL:** http://localhost:5173
> **Backend:** http://localhost:3003
> **Languages:** English (`en`), Ukrainian (`uk`)
> **Themes:** Light, Dark, System

---

## Your Role

You are a **Senior Manual QA Engineer** performing a full regression test of the WashFlow admin panel — a multi-tenant car wash management SaaS. You will systematically test every page, modal, and component for:

1. **Translations** — every visible string must exist in both EN and UK, no raw keys (e.g. `nav.dashboard`), no English leaking in UK mode and vice-versa.
2. **Theme** — every page/modal must render correctly in Light, Dark, and System modes. Check for: invisible text, broken contrast, wrong backgrounds, unstyled borders, hardcoded colors ignoring theme.
3. **Mobile View** — resize to 375px width (iPhone SE). Check for: overflow, horizontal scroll, truncated buttons, overlapping elements, unreadable text, untappable targets (<44px), broken navigation.
4. **Business Logic** — verify that forms validate correctly, CRUD operations work, permission gates hide/show elements, soft-delete/restore works, status transitions are valid, pagination works, filters apply correctly.

---

## Test Environment Setup

1. Open the app at `http://localhost:5173`
2. Login with valid credentials (email + password + tenantId)
3. For each page/modal below, repeat the full checklist in this order:
   - [ ] **EN + Light theme**
   - [ ] **UK + Light theme**
   - [ ] **EN + Dark theme**
   - [ ] **UK + Dark theme**
   - [ ] **Mobile (375px) + Light**
   - [ ] **Mobile (375px) + Dark**

---

## Global Components (test on every page)

### Header
- [ ] Hamburger menu appears only on mobile (< lg breakpoint)
- [ ] GlobalSearch (Cmd/Ctrl+K) opens, searches clients/orders/services, shows type badges — hidden on mobile
- [ ] ThemeToggle cycles: Light → Dark → System → Light (icons: Sun / Moon / Monitor)
- [ ] LanguageSwitcher toggles EN ↔ UK, all visible text updates immediately
- [ ] User info: firstName + lastName, email, truncated tenantId (click to copy — verify toast)
- [ ] Change Password button (KeyRound icon) opens ChangePasswordDialog
- [ ] Logout button works, redirects to /login

### Sidebar
- [ ] Collapsed (64px) and expanded (256px) states work
- [ ] On mobile: renders as overlay drawer with close (X) button
- [ ] Section headers: Main, Management, System, Help — translated
- [ ] Active route highlighted with bg-primary/10 text-primary
- [ ] Permission-gated items hidden for non-permitted users:
  - Main: Dashboard (no perm), Orders (ORDERS.READ), Clients (CLIENTS.READ), Vehicles (VEHICLES.READ), Services (SERVICES.READ)
  - Management: Branches (BRANCHES.READ), Work Posts (WORK_POSTS.READ), Users (USERS.READ), Roles (ROLES.READ), Workforce (WORKFORCE.READ), Subscription (TENANTS.READ)
  - System: Analytics (ANALYTICS.VIEW), Audit (AUDIT.READ)
  - Help: How To (no perm)

### ChangePasswordDialog
- [ ] Fields: currentPassword, newPassword, confirmPassword
- [ ] Validation: all required, newPassword != currentPassword, confirmPassword must match
- [ ] Success toast on change, error toast on wrong current password
- [ ] Translations for title, labels, button, error/success messages

### ConfirmDialog (used globally)
- [ ] Two variants: default (blue) and destructive (red)
- [ ] Title, message, confirm/cancel buttons translated
- [ ] Loading spinner on confirm button while processing
- [ ] ESC and backdrop click close the dialog

