## Page-by-Page Test Plan

---

### 1. Login Page (/login)

**Translations:**
- [ ] Title, subtitle, field labels (Email, Password, Tenant ID), submit button, loading state, error messages

**Theme:**
- [ ] Card centered, readable in light/dark, no invisible inputs

**Mobile:**
- [ ] Full-width card, inputs usable, submit button reachable

**Business Logic:**
- [ ] Empty fields → validation errors
- [ ] Wrong credentials → error message (no credential leak)
- [ ] Successful login → redirect to /
- [ ] Already logged in → redirect to /

---

### 2. Dashboard (/)

**Translations:**
- [ ] KPI labels: Revenue Today, Orders Today, Avg Duration, Cancel Rate, Active Clients, Occupancy Rate
- [ ] Live Operations: In Progress, Waiting, Free Work Posts, Overdue
- [ ] Branch Performance table headers
- [ ] Employee Performance table headers
- [ ] Alerts: severity labels (LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL), alert type messages
- [ ] Online Booking Stats: source labels (Internal, Web, Widget, API)
- [ ] Revenue chart title

**Theme:**
- [ ] Charts (Recharts) render with theme-appropriate colors
- [ ] KPI cards have correct background/border contrast
- [ ] Alert severity badges: color-coded correctly in both themes

**Mobile:**
- [ ] KPI cards stack vertically
- [ ] Charts are scrollable or resize appropriately
- [ ] Tables are scrollable horizontally
- [ ] Live panel doesn't overflow

**Business Logic:**
- [ ] KPI data loads (not all zeros unless truly empty)
- [ ] Branch filter on revenue chart works
- [ ] Alerts panel shows "No alerts" when empty
- [ ] Live Operations updates in real-time (WebSocket)

---

### 3. Orders Page (/orders)

**Translations:**
- [ ] Page title, "Create Order" button, table headers (client, vehicle, status, branch, date, total)
- [ ] Status badges: BOOKED, BOOKED_PENDING_CONFIRMATION, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED, CANCELLED, NO_SHOW
- [ ] Source badges: INTERNAL, WEB, WIDGET, API
- [ ] Filter labels: Status, Branch, Date From, Date To
- [ ] Pagination: "Showing X to Y of Z entries", per-page selector

**Theme:**
- [ ] Status badges have distinct colors in both themes
- [ ] Table rows alternate correctly
- [ ] Filter dropdowns styled correctly

**Mobile:**
- [ ] Table scrolls horizontally or switches to card view
- [ ] Filters collapse or stack
- [ ] Create button accessible

**Business Logic:**
- [ ] Filters apply correctly (status, branch, date range)
- [ ] Pagination works (10/20/50/100 per page)
- [ ] Table/Card view toggle works
- [ ] Click row → navigates to /orders/:id

---

### 4. Create Order (/orders/create)

**Translations:**
- [ ] Wizard step labels: Select Client, Select Vehicle, Select Services, Select Worker, Select Slot, Review
- [ ] Field labels, search placeholders, "Create Client" / "Create Vehicle" buttons
- [ ] Total duration, total amount labels
- [ ] Available slots / no slots messages
- [ ] Confirm booking button, success message

**Theme:**
- [ ] Wizard step indicator styled correctly
- [ ] Time slot buttons contrast properly
- [ ] Selected service items highlighted visually

**Mobile:**
- [ ] Wizard steps navigable (back/next buttons reachable)
- [ ] Service list scrollable
- [ ] Time slots grid doesn't overflow

**Business Logic:**
- [ ] Step 0: Client search works, "+ Create Client" opens inline dialog, selecting client proceeds
- [ ] Step 1: Vehicle list filters by selected client, "+ Create Vehicle" works
- [ ] Step 2: Services list shows with price/duration, total updates on selection
- [ ] Step 3: Worker selection optional ("Any Worker" option)
- [ ] Step 4: Date picker → available slots load, selecting slot proceeds
- [ ] Step 5: Review shows all selections, "Confirm Booking" creates order
- [ ] Success → redirect to order detail or orders list
- [ ] Cannot skip steps (next disabled until step is valid)

**Quick-create Client Dialog (in step 0):**
- [ ] Fields: firstName, lastName, email, phone
- [ ] Validation: required fields
- [ ] Created client auto-selected
- [ ] Translations for all fields and buttons

**Quick-create Vehicle Dialog (in step 1):**
- [ ] Fields: make (required), licensePlate, model, color, year
- [ ] Created vehicle auto-selected
- [ ] Translations

