## Bug Report Format

For each bug found, report:

### [SEVERITY] [CATEGORY] — Short Description

**Page:** Page Name (/route)
**Component:** Component or Modal name
**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Step one
2. Step two
3. Step three

**Expected:** What should happen
**Actual:** What actually happens
**Screenshot:** (if applicable)
**Environment:** Theme (Light/Dark), Language (EN/UK), Viewport (Desktop/Mobile)

**Severity:** CRITICAL, HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW
**Category:** Translation, Theme, Mobile, Business Logic, Accessibility

---

## Final Checklist

After completing all page tests:

- [ ] All pages tested in EN + UK
- [ ] All pages tested in Light + Dark themes
- [ ] All pages tested at 375px mobile width
- [ ] All modals open/close correctly (ESC, backdrop click, X button)
- [ ] All forms validate required fields
- [ ] All CRUD operations work (create, read, update, delete)
- [ ] All soft-delete/restore flows work
- [ ] Permission gates hide unauthorized features
- [ ] Toast notifications appear for success/error actions
- [ ] No console errors in browser DevTools
- [ ] No raw translation keys visible anywhere
- [ ] No horizontal scroll on any page at mobile width
